stories.title: Upbeat Australia defeat India by 93 runs, level series
stories.summary:
Australia annihilated the Indian bowlers in the first session to make
338/4 in 50 overs and then demolished the top order of the Indian batting
line up, to bowl them out for 245 in 45 overs
